    "body": "The work area information on Linux is received by reading the `_NET_WORKAREA` hint provided by window manager, if the values are wrong, then it is an issue of the window manager, there is no way for Electron to know the correct value.\r\n\r\nI'm closing this since we are unable to fix this on Electron's side."
